ZH: 农耕是农民种植农作物和养殖家禽家畜的行为。
EN: Farming is the act of planting crops and raising livestock by farmers.

ZH: 在古代，农耕是人们生活的主要方式。
EN: In ancient times, farming was the main way of life for people.

ZH: 农耕需要艰苦劳动和耐心。
EN: Farming requires hard work and patience.

ZH: 他的一生都致力于农耕工作。
EN: His whole life was dedicated to farming work.

ZH: 农耕对环境和自然资源有着重要影响。
EN: Farming has a significant impact on the environment and natural resources.

ZH: 农耕技术的提升可以提高农作物产量。
EN: Improvements in farming techniques can increase crop yields.

ZH: 农耕是实现粮食安全的重要手段之一。
EN: Farming is one of the important means to achieve food security.

ZH: 农耕文化在中国有着悠久的历史。
EN: Farming culture has a long history in China.

ZH: 农耕的季节可以根据不同的气候变化而有所不同。
EN: The farming seasons can vary according to different climate changes.

ZH: 在现代社会中，农耕仍然是重要的产业之一。
EN: In modern society, farming is still one of the important industries.

ZH: 农耕经验传承自祖辈至今。
EN: Farming experience has been passed down from ancestors to the present day.

ZH: 对于农耕来说，保护土地是至关重要的。
EN: Protecting the land is crucial for farming.

ZH: 农耕需要适应市场需求，以增加农产品的竞争力。
EN: Farming needs to adapt to market demand to increase the competitiveness of agricultural products.

ZH: 现代化的农耕方法可以提高工作效率。
EN: Modern farming methods can improve work efficiency.

ZH: 农民一家人共同参与农耕工作。
EN: The whole family of farmers participates in farming work.

ZH: 农耕不仅是一种经济活动，还是一种生活方式。
EN: Farming is not only an economic activity but also a way of life.

ZH: 农耕的过程需要根据不同的作物进行施肥、灌溉等一系列工作。
EN: The farming process requires a series of activities such as fertilizing and irrigating according to different crops.

ZH: 农耕能够创造就业机会，提供农民的收入来源。
EN: Farming can create job opportunities and provide income sources for farmers.

ZH: 农耕技术的进步可以推动农业现代化发展。
EN: The advancement of farming technology can promote modernization in agriculture.

ZH: 农耕是农村社会的基石。
EN: Farming is the cornerstone of rural society.
